#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - validation of IP addresses - a valid IP address
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"format": "ipv4"}
--- json
"192.168.0.1"


=== Test 2 - validation of IP addresses - an IP address with too many components
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"127.0.0.0.1"


=== Test 3 - validation of IP addresses - an IP address with out-of-range values
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"256.256.256.256"


=== Test 4 - validation of IP addresses - an IP address without 4 components
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"127.0"


=== Test 5 - validation of IP addresses - an IP address as an integer
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"0x7f000001"


